snippet.title: CODE Bunny - Gameplay & Release Date Trailer [OUT NOW!]
snippet.description:
Hop into a futuristic world of bunnies to experience high speed 2D Action!
Play as two characters - Axel and Hazel - as they face the group Mad Bunny and uncover a hidden conspiracy...

Official Game Page: https://lavie-azure.itch.io/code-bunny
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Lavie_Azure

Title: CODE Bunny
Developer: Team Seventh Star
Platforms: PC - itch.io
Genre: Action
Players: 1
Release Date: September 22, 2023
Price: $10.00 USD

The game will also have its Final Demo at #SAGE23 (https://sagexpo.org/) on September 1st to 8th.
